<HL>
   Pier 1 Imports' Sales Increase
</HL>
<DATE>
06/14/90
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE C6
</SO>
<CO>
   PIR
</CO>
<LP>
   FORT WORTH, Texas -- Pier 1 Imports Inc., a specialty
retailer, said sales for its first quarter ended June 2
increased 22% to $138.4 million from $113.9 million a year
earlier. Sales at stores open at least a year rose 5.5%.
